rComments: I did not find this teacher very clear in his explications, I had to support the class with the textbook in order to pass. He makes his exams the same as the revision which makes it ''easy'' to pass, but for those who actually wanted to learn will need to put in extra effort

Great prof. Assignments can be hard and are designed to test you judgement. Exams are a piece of cake if you practice exactly what he tells you to practice.   Do the readings or you will be lost in class.  The book (binder) is well written and will teach you so much about accounting.
